{
    "version": "https://jsonfeed.org/version/1",
    "title": "riversea的个人博客 • All posts by \"设计模式\" tag",
    "description": "亿点点心得",
    "home_page_url": "https://blog.riversea.top",
    "items": [
        {
            "id": "https://blog.riversea.top/2024/03/29/javaproxy/",
            "url": "https://blog.riversea.top/2024/03/29/javaproxy/",
            "title": "代理",
            "date_published": "2024-03-29T12:13:09.000Z",
            "content_html": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"\\assets\\js\\Meting.min.js\"></script><h1 id=\"代理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#代理\">#</a> 🥳代理</h1>\n<p>什么是代理呢。举个🌰子，你要去买房子，但你并不知道房子的一些细节，比如地段，是否有升值空间，安保好不好等等。所以你可以找一个熟悉房地产产业的一个专家，也就是我们所说的<strong>中介</strong>来咨询如何买房子。他可以根据你的需求提供你具体的信息，然后你就可以判断买哪些房子。客户不会直接接触房子，而是直接访问中介，中介再提供房子的信息。这个中介就是我们所说的<strong>代理</strong>。在代理模式中，客户端不会直接接触目标对象，而是访问代理对象，代理对象再去访问目标对象。</p>\n<p>在代理中有如下术语：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>目标 (类) 对象：被代理 (类) 对象代理的对 (类) 对象。可以理解为上述例子的房子</li>\n<li>代理 (类) 对象：代理目标 (类) 对象的 (类) 对象。可以理解为上述例子的中介</li>\n</ul>\n<p>使用代理模有如下优点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>提供安全访问。我们使用代理对象来帮我们过滤客户端的非法请求，从而保证了系统安全。</li>\n<li>代码增强。我们可以在代理对象中提供一些额外的功能。例如：日志，格式转换等等。</li>\n<li>低耦合。让业务类更加注重业务，一些非业务的代码则交给代理类实现。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>为了保证代理类和目标类一一对应，也就是说，当我们访问代理类的时候，代理类能精确访问到目标类的某个功能，所以我们使用继承和实现约束代理类和目标类的关系来实现代理</p>\n<h1 id=\"静态代理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#静态代理\">#</a> 🌈静态代理</h1>\n<p>首先我们来介绍一下静态代理。顾名思义，静态代理是指，早在编码阶段的时候就将代理的双方确定好了并使用硬编码保存在了硬盘中。</p>\n<p>前面提到，实现代理有继承和实现两种方式，我们以订单的例子来进行下面的介绍。</p>\n<h2 id=\"继承\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#继承\">#</a> 继承</h2>\n<p>我们首先实现  <code>OrderService</code>  这个类，让他作为目标业务类：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderService</span>&#123;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">generate</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;订单已生成&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">detail</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;订单信息如下：******&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">modify</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;订单已修改&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>接下来我们实现代理类  <code>OrderServiceProxy</code>  ，为了约束代理类，我们继承这个目标业务类  <code>OrderService</code>  ：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderServiceProxy</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderService</span>&#123;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">generate</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;客户要求产生新的订单&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">super</span>.generate();<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">detail</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;客户要求获得订单详情&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">super</span>.detail();<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">modify</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;客户要求修改订单信息&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">super</span>.modify();<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>我们让这个代理类实现日志功能，来记录每次请求的请求内容。</p>\n<p>下面你就可以编写主类来尝试访问代理类。请注意，不要直接访问目标类。</p>\n<p>通过继承的方式实现静态代理是不是非常简单，但你有没有想过一个问题。我们实现一个代理非常简单，只需要写一个代理类。但如果是 100 个、1000 个呢？我们就将写上百上千个代理类，这将会导致类爆炸难以维护。</p>\n<p>在软件设计有个规定：<strong>组合优于继承</strong>。所以，下面我们来介绍通过组合和实现的方式来实现代理</p>\n<h2 id=\"实现\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#实现\">#</a> 实现</h2>\n<p>要使用实现，我们必须提供一个接口：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderService</span> &#123;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">     * 生成订单</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">     */</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">generate</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span>;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">     * 查看订单详情</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">     */</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">detail</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span>;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">     * 修改订单</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">     */</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">modify</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>我们使用  <code>OrderServiceImpl</code>  来实现这个接口：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderServiceImpl</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderService</span> &#123;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">generate</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;订单已生成&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">detail</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;订单信息如下：******&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">modify</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;订单已修改&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>接下来我们实现代理类  <code>OrderServiceProxy</code> ，为了约束代理类，我们必须实现  <code>OrderService</code>  接口：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderServiceProxy</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderService</span>&#123;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> OrderService orderService;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OrderServiceProxy</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(OrderService orderService)</span>&#123;<br>        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">this</span>.orderService = orderService;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">generate</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;客户要求产生新的订单&quot;</span>);<br>        orderService.generate();<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">detail</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;客户要求获得订单详情&quot;</span>);<br>        orderService.detail();<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">modify</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;客户要求修改订单信息&quot;</span>);<br>        orderService.modify();<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>我们将  <code>OrderService</code>  组合至代理类中。且我们使用了多态，让其在运行的时候动态的传值，达到一个代理类可以动态的代理同一个接口下的多个目标类，避免了类爆炸的发生，这就是组合的魅力。</p>\n<p>现在你可以尝试在主类中访问这个代理类，同时你可以提供多个目标类给代理类观察效果。</p>\n<p>尽管静态代理已经能实现代理模式了，但仍然  <code>jdk</code>  仍然提供了另外一种方式来动态的实现代理，那就是<strong>动态代理</strong>。</p>\n<h1 id=\"动态代理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#动态代理\">#</a> 🔥动态代理</h1>\n<p><code>jdk</code>  提供了一种基于反射的动态代理方式来实现代理方式。该方法不用硬编码代理类，而是在内存中动态生成代理对象。实际上，动态代理仍然使用的是实现接口的方式来实现代理。实现  <code>jdk</code>  的动态代理需要如下的类：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>Proxy</code> ：代理类的基类，所以的代理类都继承于这个类</li>\n<li><code>InvocationHandler</code> ：调用处理器接口。用于执行目标类的方法。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>我们任然保留上述例子中的  <code>OrderService</code>  接口和  <code>OrderServiceImpl</code>  实现类</p>\n<p>下面我们来实现  <code>InvocationHandler</code> ：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderInvocationHandler</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InvocationHandler</span> &#123;<br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> OrderService orderService; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//我们同样让其在运行时动态绑定。</span><br><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OrderInvocationHandler</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(OrderService orderService)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">this</span>.orderService = orderService;<br>    &#125;<br>    <br>\t<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">\t\tproxy: 动态生成的代理类对象</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">\t\tmethod：目标类的某个方法对象</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">\t\targs：方法参数</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">\t*/</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> Object <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">invoke</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(Object proxy, Method method, Object[] args)</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throws</span> Throwable &#123;<br>        <span class=\"hljs-type\">long</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">begin</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\">=</span> System.currentTimeMillis(); <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//计算开始时间</span><br>        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 执行目标对象的目标方法</span><br>        <span class=\"hljs-type\">Object</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">res</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\">=</span> method.invoke(orderService, args);<br>        <span class=\"hljs-type\">long</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">end</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\">=</span> System.currentTimeMillis(); <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//计算结束时间</span><br>        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;耗时&quot;</span> + (end - begin) + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;毫秒&quot;</span>); <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//打印结束时间</span><br>        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> res;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>InvocationHandler</code>  只有一个抽象方法： <code>public Object invoke(Object proxy, Method method, Object[] args) throws Throwable</code> 。所以只需要实现这个方法即可。你可能已经发现了，实现了  <code>InvocationHandler</code>  接口的  <code>OrderInvocationHandler </code> 类用来调用目标类。</p>\n<p>下面让我们来实现代理对象：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs java\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">OrderService</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">orderService</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\">=</span> (OrderService) Proxy.newProxyInstance(ClassLoader.getSystemClassLoader(), <br>                                                                 OrderServiceImpl.class.getInterfaces(),<br>                                                                 <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderInvocationHandler</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">OrderServiceImpl</span>()));<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>我们使用  <code>Proxy</code>  的静态方法  <code>newProxyInstance</code>  来创建一个代理类对象，该方法有如下参数：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>ClassLoader classLoader</code> ：类加载器，用于将代理对象加载进内存中。</li>\n<li><code>Class&lt;?&gt;[] interfaces</code> ：目标类的接口字节码对象数组。前面提到，动态代理仍然使用实现接口的方式来代理，所以我们仍需提供接口</li>\n<li><code>InvocationHandler h</code> ：调用处理器。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>通过该方法创建的代理对象，默认是  <code>Object</code>  类型，但我们可以使用接口强转至我们需要的类型，来使用里面的方法。接下来就可以调用我们刚刚创建的代理类对象的方法了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"原理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#原理\">#</a> 原理</h2>\n<p>实际上， <code>jdk</code>  的动态代理原理是创建了一个存放在  <code>jdk.proxy数字.$proxy数字</code>  包下的代理对象。</p>\n<h3 id=\"获取动态代理类对象\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#获取动态代理类对象\">#</a> 获取动态代理类对象</h3>\n<p>在  <code>jvm</code>  参数中添加如下参数：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight ini\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs ini\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">-Dsun.misc.ProxyGenerator.saveGeneratedFiles</span>=<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>运行创建动态类对象后。毫无疑问，你将在该目录上看到一个  <code>jdk</code>  的目录，让我们点进去，你将会看到一个  <code>class</code>  文件，这就是在内存中生成的动态代理类对象。</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "设计模式"
            ]
        }
    ]
}